          "description": "*Not a review of the staff, who are all 5 star and I adore!*\n\nIt's been at least six months that several smoke alarms have been chirping low battery very loudly throughout this large office. I feel so much for the staff, especially reception, who has to listen to this all day. Could management disrespect their staff more than to go so long failing to do such a simple repair that would have such a big impact?  (Also not fun being a migraine patient and having to listen to this).\n\nAnd this is besides the fact that the smoke alarms haven't been in operation, surely a fire code violation (hint hint).",
